text: Don Mansale (born 10 October 1991) is a Vanuatuan footballer who plays as a striker for Tupuji Imere F.C. in the Port Vila Football League. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Vanuatuan footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:Vanuatu international footballers Category:Tafea F.C. players
